---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Centro de Salud Holistica — Dr. Joaquin Ipinza"
  description="Centro de odontologia holistica y biologica en Santiago. Eliminacion de amalgamas, implantes ceramicoss, biomimetica y mas. Los Dominicos, Las Condes."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900 via-emerald-800 to-neutral-900">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-teal-400 via-emerald-900 to-neutral-900"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-8">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="text-sm text-white/90 font-medium">Centro pionero de salud holistica en Chile</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Belleza es habitarte<br />
          <span class="text-teal-400">en armonia</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/75 mb-10 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Odontologia libre de metales pesados, implantes ceramicoss biocompatibles y un enfoque que considera tu cuerpo, tu mente y tu vida.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-12">
          <a href="/contacto" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-teal-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-teal-600 transition-all hover:shadow-lg no-underline">
            Agendar mi primera consulta
          </a>
          <a href="/libro" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-all no-underline">
            📖 Leer el libro gratuito
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-1">🌿</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-white/70">Libre de mercurio</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-1">🦴</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-white/70">Implantes ceramicoss</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-1">🔬</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-white/70">Protocolo IAOMT</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-1">🌍</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-white/70">Pacientes internacionales</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICIOS -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 bg-teal-50 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Servicios clinicos</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-neutral-900 mb-4">Tratamientos holisticos integrales</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Cada tratamiento se disena considerando tu biocompatibilidad, tu historia medica y tu bienestar completo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/servicios/eliminacion-amalgamas" class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-teal-500 transition-colors"><span class="text-2xl">⚕️</span></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors">Eliminacion de Amalgamas</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Protocolo IAOMT certificado. Remocion segura de empastes con mercurio siguiendo estandares internacionales.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 group-hover:text-teal-800">Protocolo IAOMT →</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/servicios/implantes-ceramicos" class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-teal-500 transition-colors"><span class="text-2xl">🦴</span></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors">Implantes Ceramicoss</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Implantes 100% libres de titanio. Ceramica biocompatible que se integra naturalmente con tu hueso.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 group-hover:text-teal-800">Sin metales pesados →</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/servicios/odontologia-biomimetica" class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-teal-500 transition-colors"><span class="text-2xl">✨</span></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors">Odontologia Biomimetica</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Conservacion maxima del diente natural. Restauraciones que imitan la estructura y funcion del diente original.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 group-hover:text-teal-800">Conserva tu diente →</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/servicios/tratamiento-atm" class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-teal-500 transition-colors"><span class="text-2xl">💆</span></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors">Tratamiento de ATM</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Dolor de mandibula, cabeza o cuello. Enfoque integral con ortopedia, relajacion y terapia neural.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 group-hover:text-teal-800">Sin dolor cronico →</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/servicios/ozonoterapia" class="group bg-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-teal-500 transition-colors"><span class="text-2xl">🌬️</span></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors">Ozonoterapia Dental</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Propiedades antimicrobianas naturales. Esterilizacion sin antibioticos, aceleracion de la cicatrizacion.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 group-hover:text-teal-800">Biocompatible →</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/servicios" class="group bg-emerald-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-emerald-200 hover:border-emerald-400 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-emerald-500 transition-colors"><span class="text-2xl">+</span></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Ver todos los servicios</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Odontologia general, estetica facial, acupuntura, nutricion y mas tratamientos complementarios.</p>
          <div class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-600 group-hover:text-emerald-800">17 servicios disponibles →</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LIBRO -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-50 to-teal-50/30">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 bg-teal-50 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">📖 Contenido educativo gratuito</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-neutral-900 mb-4">Salud Evolutiva:<br />el libro que cambia perspectiva</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">129 paginas basadas en evidencia cientifica que explican por que tenemos las enfermedades que tenemos — y que hacer al respecto. Escrito para que cualquier persona lo entienda.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-5 h-5 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-teal-600 text-xs">✓</span></span><span class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Gratuito para leer online, completo y sin registro</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-5 h-5 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-teal-600 text-xs">✓</span></span><span class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">5 capitulos sobre evolucion, nutricion y salud bucal</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="w-5 h-5 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"><span class="text-teal-600 text-xs">✓</span></span><span class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Ilustraciones y referencias cientificas</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/libro" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-emerald-800 transition-colors no-underline">📖 Leer el libro completo →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-neutral-200 p-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-36 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-700 to-teal-600 rounded-lg mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-center text-white">
                <div class="text-xs font-bold leading-tight px-2">SALUD</div>
                <div class="text-xl font-bold leading-tight">EVOLUTIVA</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2">Salud Evolutiva</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">Dr. Joaquin Ipinza Hofmann</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-xs text-neutral-400">
              <span>📄 129 paginas</span><span>•</span><span>📊 38,000 palabras</span><span>•</span><span>🆓 Gratis</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOBRE -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-100 to-teal-50 rounded-3xl aspect-square flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center px-8">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center text-6xl">👨‍⚕️</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-emerald-700 font-medium">Foto profesional<br />por confirmar</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 bg-teal-50 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">👨‍⚕️ El Doctor</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-neutral-900 mb-4">Dr. Joaquin Ipinza Hofmann</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Cirujano dentista de la Universidad de Chile, con especializacion en Periodoncia e Implantologia Buco-Maxilo-Facial. Formado ademas en Loma Linda University, California. Miembro activo de la Sociedad de Periodoncia de Chile y de la Holistic Dental Association.</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Su busqueda lo llevo mas alla de la odontologia convencional: estudio pueblos originarios, su alimentacion ancestral y su salud bucal. De ahi nacio su enfoque holistico — que integra nutricion, acupuntura, ozonoterapia y una vision integral del ser humano.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
            <span class="bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-700 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">DDS — Universidad de Chile</span>
            <span class="bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-700 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Especialista en Periodoncia</span>
            <span class="bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-700 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Loma Linda University</span>
            <span class="bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-700 text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Protocolo IAOMT</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/sobre" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-700 font-semibold hover:text-teal-900 no-underline">Conoce mas sobre el doctor →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- BLOG PREVIEW -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-sm font-medium text-teal-600 bg-teal-50 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">📰 Blog</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-neutral-900 mb-4">Artículos sobre salud evolutiva</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Contenido educativo del Dr. Ipinza sobre odontología holística, nutrición evolutiva y bienestar.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/blog/" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">📚</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700">Guía de alimentación evolutiva</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Aprende qué alimentos favorecen tu salud bucal según la evolución.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🦷</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700">Prevención de caries natural</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Estrategias naturales para prevenir caries sin químicos agresivos.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/" class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-teal-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-4">💆</div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-neutral-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-700">Estrés y salud dental</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500">Conexión entre bruxismo, estrés y problemas mandibulares.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/blog/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-700 font-semibold hover:text-teal-900 no-underline">
          Ver todos los artículos →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-800 to-teal-700">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-4">¿Quieres empezar tu tratamiento?</h2>
      <p class="text-white/75 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">Agenda tu primera consulta. Sin compromiso. Escuchamos tu historia completa antes de proponer cualquier tratamiento.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contacto" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-emerald-800 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-teal-50 transition-colors no-underline text-lg">Agendar mi consulta →</a>
        <a href="/servicios" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 text-white font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors no-underline text-lg">Ver servicios</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>